The paper deals with the estimation of position and orientation using millimeter wave signals, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The use of large antenna arrays and signal processing algorithms also falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). The paper specifically focuses on millimeter wave signals, which is a subfield of multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper also discusses the use of scatterers and algorithms for estimation, which are topics related to computer vision (cs.CV).
